original_title: Stone Hits Live: The Very Best of Angie Stone
overview: Roots and R&B singer Angie Stone delivers a live offering of her greatest hits, with a soulful rendering of her most popular songs and accompaniment from Alicia Keys, Greg Collier, and Raymond Hinton. Stone effortlessly evokes a lost era of classic R&B with a set list that includes "Wish I Didn't Miss You" and "Brotha."
title: Stone Hits Live: The Very Best of Angie Stone
